Description: Printed books, newspapers, pictures and other products of the printing industry; manuscripts, typescripts and plans

Subentries.Description: Newspapers, journals and periodicals, whether or not illustrated or containing advertising material:
Newspaper supplements printed by a gravure process
Newspapers appearing less than four times per week
Other business and professional journals and periodicals (including single issues tied together for shipping purposes)
Other (including single issues tied together for shipping purposes)
